{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e35cf55b9f","title":"给续范亭的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e35180aa36","index":0,"year":1943,"month":12,"day":4,"articleId":"e35cf55b9f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fd97a863f0","type":"paragraph","text":"给续范亭的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"e35cf55b9f"},{"id":"378d09f8e2","type":"paragraph","text":"（1943年12月4日范亭同志：大示及诗拜读，洋粉拜领，江青当遵示照服。贵体虽有起色，但看东西仍不宜太多，请加注意。邓先生西北人望，调护国共关系，出力甚多，此次南行，讲了许多好话，我们心中感谢他。催此次见面，似不满足，因我们未谈具体办法。其实我们毫无具体办法，例如撒消封锁，承认边区，恢复新四等等，除听候国民党解决外，我们方面是毫无办法的。边区周围情况仍紧，惟国际环境日好，日寇又有进攻之势，时局或可不走向决裂。明年春夏尚有一关，过了此关，或有好转之望。我如常，一年未生大感冒，算一幸事。敬频起居安畅！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"e35cf55b9f"},{"id":"3cd8f14353","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"e35cf55b9f"},{"id":"c8aa2a7ed8","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月四日Ui]指邓宝册，当时任晋陕缓边区总司令。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"e35cf55b9f"}],"page":{"id":"21a6ab6ae6","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"e35cf55b9f","start":254,"end":254}}}},"__N_SSG":true}